<li>打开网页。</li>
<li><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>l</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Ctrl+f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.77777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span></span></span></span> 搜索<code>repo:</code>，应该只有一个。</li>
<li>再 <code>repo:</code> 下面的输入框输入你的博客用户的仓库，例如我的就是 <code>GarbageBlog/Garbage.github.io</code></li>
<li>往下走一点，看到 <code>Choose the mapping between blog posts and GitHub issues.</code> 这行字，这里是要你选择 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>b</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Github Issues</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault">h</span><span class="mord mathdefault">u</span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault">u</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span></span></span></span> 的配置方式，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="red"><mtext>除非你明确它是什么意思，否则就用第一个</mtext></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{red}\text{除非你明确它是什么意思，否则就用第一个}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text" style="color:red;"><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:red;">除非你明确它是什么意思，否则就用第一个</span></span></span></span></span> 。</li>
