<h2 id="23-使用在博客中使用-utterances-评论系统">2.3 使用——在博客中使用 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">utterances</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">u</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span></span></span></span> 评论系统</h2>
<p><s>这地方有点烦，加之要上网课的我没时间，就挤一挤时间，最近把它更完！</s></p>
<p>由于 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">utterances</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.61508em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">u</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault">t</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span></span></span></span> 评论系统并不属于 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Gridea</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span></span></span></span> 自带的评论系统，所以……</p>
<p><strong>你需要自己手动装代码！！！</strong></p>
<p><s>这里告诉大家一个不正经的代码安装位置，就是主题 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mo>&gt;</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-&gt;</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">&gt;</span></span></span></span> 底部信息的代码框，复制到那里就行了。</s></p>
<p><s>这样是测你的代码有没有用的好办法。</s></p>
<p>接下来正经点，我们要把评论代码装在文章模板的某一个位置，就是仅对你的文章才生效的地方，以我的 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>N</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">NexT</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span> 主题为例。</p>
<p>首先我们来到自己的网站，进入一个文章界面，翻到底部。</p>
<p>然后，<strong>右键你想插入评论系统的地方（一般放在文章正下方，注意要在文章正文的上面下面，不要出去了，出去就没用了）点那个“检查”或“检查元素”，浏览器弹出对话框</strong></p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://GarbageBlog.github.io/post-images/1582701239810.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>接着去数<strong>高亮的那一行</strong>离**底部的<code>&lt;/body&gt;</code>**中间差了几个<code>&lt;/div&gt;</code>，记下来。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://GarbageBlog.github.io/post-images/1582702097106.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>例如我这里就有四个。</p>
<p>接下来，进入你存放 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Gridea</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span></span></span></span> 数据的文件夹，依次打开“themes -&gt; [你要使用的模板] -&gt; templates” 其中[你要使用的模板]替换为你要使用的模板名。</p>
<p>然后用可编辑的程序打开“post.ejs”，然后找到 <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> 往上数你记得数字个 <code>&lt;/div&gt;</code>，在那里粘贴2.2中获取的代码…… <s>（终于有用了）</s></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="red"><mstyle mathsize="2.488em"><mtext>修改前请备份！！！</mtext></mstyle></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{red}\Huge\text{修改前请备份！！！}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.7001250399999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text sizing reset-size6 size11" style="color:red;"><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:red;">修改前请备份！！！</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>然后记得保存，去 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Gridea</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">G</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mord mathdefault">e</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span></span></span></span> 上同步。</p>
